Hi Team,
I am working with the following API to create a contact if it doesn’t exist and update it if it does:
`<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v3/objects/contacts/batch/upsert>`
However, I am encountering the following error:
```{
    "status": "error",
    "message": "Unable to perform update/upsert by non-unique 0-1 property email in portal ID XXXXXXX",
    "correlationId": "XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX",
    "category": "VALIDATION_ERROR"
}```
The body I am sending is:
```{
    "inputs": [
        {
            "idProperty": "email",
            "id": "<mailto:abc@gmail.com|abc@gmail.com>",
            "properties": {
                "phone": "123"
            }
        }
    ]
}```
Could anyone please guide me on how to resolve this issue?
Thanks

